{"tid":1926032,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［甜故］老婆仔⋯⋯嘻嘻⋯⋯老婆仔⋯⋯嘻嘻⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-03-14T21:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T19:15:52.000Z","uid":42927,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d59189c997561a53b66be8607fa7497e224d7f6","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:22:49.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯"},{"pid":"153ec649c5c74d61c16c6c322e64eb0f92f81b99","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:23:25.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪⋯⋯啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯"},{"pid":"1ed22dbb6adeca7c0a1617a3db4d6d093f510949","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:28:45.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嘻⋯⋯老婆仔啊⋯⋯你副body真係好得啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「你真係好靚啊老婆仔⋯⋯啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯唔好⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「老婆仔啊⋯⋯啊⋯⋯你真係好好屌⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯求下你⋯⋯放過我啦⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嘻⋯⋯我就快唔得啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「喂呀⋯⋯啊⋯⋯」"},{"pid":"9e3d157c33eb07dcc3761725910c2eb7e41305d9","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:29:00.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯"},{"pid":"2bfccf4867ad63abed7291b06db0d1ea73e9e1dc","tid":1926032,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d651b7ee0d5516123a8ad5aeef5db3fbfaffa6f","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:39:59.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「啊⋯⋯老婆仔⋯⋯我射入去好冇呀？」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯唔好呀⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯求下你啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「咁你同我講聲，你好愛我啦好冇呀？」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「唔講我就射入去。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔好啊！嗚⋯⋯會有BB㗎⋯⋯你放過我啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「真係唔肯講？我射入去㗎啦。」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我刻意地加快了抽插，每次都用力把陰莖插到底，頂進這個女孩的子宮深處。<br />\n<br />\n女孩正被我用狗仔式蹂躪著，望住她又圓又大的屁股，我的手指不禁在她那臀肉下陷著。<br />\n<br />\n而耳邊只迴盪著她的淒厲的啜泣聲和我倆肉體碰撞的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「啊⋯⋯老婆仔⋯⋯我射入去好冇呀？」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯唔好呀⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯求下你啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「咁你同我講聲，你好愛我啦好冇呀？」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「唔講我就射入去。」<br />\n<br />\n「唔好啊！嗚⋯⋯會有BB㗎⋯⋯你放過我啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「真係唔肯講？我射入去㗎啦。」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我刻意地加快了抽插，每次都用力把陰莖插到底，頂進這個女孩的子宮深處。<br />\n<br />\n女孩正被我用狗仔式蹂躪著，望住她又圓又大的屁股，我的手指不禁在她那臀肉"},{"pid":"fad6c2cefc6ac8012c472c0dd619035592fdd413","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:49:23.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「老婆仔啊⋯⋯快啲講啦⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯唔⋯⋯唔好⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n見她只懂得哭哭啼啼，我便裝作生氣，慍慍的道：「仲唔講！」<br />\n<br />\n然後我便很用力的把手打向她的屁股。<br />\n<br />\n啪！<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯唔好打啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「講呀！講你好愛我呀！」<br />\n<br />\n接著，我又朝着她的屁股拍打了數下。<br />\n<br />\n啪！<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯啊！」<br />\n<br />\n啪！<br />\n<br />\n「唔好啊⋯⋯點解啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪！<br />\n<br />\n「啊！啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪！<br />\n<br />\n「啊！唔⋯⋯唔⋯⋯唔好啊⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪！<br />\n<br />\n「仲講唔講？」"},{"pid":"52053fc33c264589cd4aaa3871155bd3ca789808","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T21:56:45.000Z","msg":"「我好愛你呀！啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n她的聲線有點顫抖，迷人的身軀也在微微抖震着。<br />\n<br />\n「愛我就好啦老婆仔⋯⋯嘻⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我的陰莖還插在她又緊又暖的小穴，輕輕蠕動著。<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我把身子向前靠著，貼著她的光滑的背脊，感受她的體溫，然後柔柔的親吻她的後頸。<br />\n<br />\n「我都愛你⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪⋯⋯"},{"pid":"807c01dfac7f95d94d0a50279e5c694460bb47cb","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:02:27.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「我真係好愛你啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n然後，我捉她的腰，加快了抽插的速度。<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n而她似是察覺了異樣，便大聲向我喊道：「喂呀！你⋯⋯啊⋯⋯你話我講完就唔射入去嘅⋯⋯唔⋯⋯唔好啊⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我一聲不發，只專注着眼前的運動。<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯喂呀⋯⋯呀！」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「嗚⋯⋯嗚⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n「嗯⋯⋯唔⋯⋯唔⋯⋯」"},{"pid":"8fa5d2723ac2551a3b6e340a3cfcabf1e1cde310","tid":1926032,"uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:04:49.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></span>"},{"pid":"2bf090f7f553ee2d09811a7b88b06cac07e63b03","tid":1926032,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:10:09.000Z","msg":"屌,咁撚快交貨"},{"pid":"a6303d9e989f20af877e9fb7b1435969f9cc960f","tid":1926032,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:11:07.000Z","msg":"終於出文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0add5fe6c49a59f2fb660650648ee46608285d8","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:12:45.000Z","msg":"最後，我把大量精液射進了這個女孩的體內。<br />\n<br />\n接著，便拿了一條繩圈着她的頸部，把她勒緊直到斷氣，再把這個被我勒斃的女孩分屍了。<br />\n<br />\n內臟和殘肢，我都用不同的方式處理掉。<br />\n<br />\n確定沒有人知道是我姦殺了她。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n老婆仔⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n唔知下一個老婆仔係邊個呢？嘻～嘻～<br />\n<br />\n係咪你呢？<br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n老婆仔我愛你呀⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n你愛唔愛我呀？<br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻⋯⋯"},{"pid":"2f17ecfbe5b21c80c206f0dbb0345b969c327da9","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa5d2723ac2551a3b6e340a3cfcabf1e1cde310","tid":1926032,"uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:04:49.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:13:13.000Z","msg":"冇錯！完！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7893af2e9d233b3a0fb3a0cd56939e4df5ebb37b","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:14:31.000Z","msg":"唔知點解有一個位置會重覆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果令大家好難睇<br />\n真係要講返句唔好意思"},{"pid":"2a9509a85176710a08fe37ada7b65a2bf327ccc0","tid":1926032,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f17ecfbe5b21c80c206f0dbb0345b969c327da9","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa5d2723ac2551a3b6e340a3cfcabf1e1cde310","tid":1926032,"uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:04:49.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪啪<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:13:13.000Z","msg":"冇錯！完！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:14:51.000Z","msg":"又咁快完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62c46fde6fe01ebd664955d7c1016a09dcfd1c0","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a9509a85176710a08fe37ada7b65a2bf327ccc0","tid":1926032,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f17ecfbe5b21c80c206f0dbb0345b969c327da9","tid":1926032,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa5d2723ac2551a3b6e340a3cfcabf1e1cde310","tid":1926032,"uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T22:04:49.000Z","msg":"